	<h1 class="title">《三体》得了雨果奖，但我依然不看好它的电影版</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4698/small/4698.jpg?1418028103" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">magasa </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-24 10:04:58 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13917/medium/13917.jpg?1440380121" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13917" data-title="《《三体》得了雨果奖，但我依然不看好它的电影版》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13917/medium/13917.jpg?1440380121" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13917.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
